---
// src/pages/now.astro
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Now" description="What Polarity Lab is focused on right now.">
  <div class="now-page">
    <div class="now-header">
      <p class="now-label">Now</p>
      <p class="now-date">April 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="now-body">

      <section class="now-section">
        <h2>Primary focus</h2>
        <p>
          Closing the first Integrity Delta proof contract. The IΔ pilot is complete: five cases,
          measurable at the layer level, showing clinical AI suppressing its own correct diagnosis
          under adversarial pressure. The next step is a validation study at scale, which produces
          the paper, plants the citation trail, and makes the methodology credible to institutional buyers.
        </p>
        <p>
          Every other resource decision at the lab is downstream of this one milestone.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="now-section">
        <h2>Active instruments</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>
            <strong>Integrity Delta</strong> — pilot complete. Validation study design in progress.
            First assessment target identified.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Cosmos</strong> — running. The counter-environment for executive function is
            operational. Ongoing as both a working tool and the proof-of-concept for the return.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Proximity Index</strong> — methodology in development for Providence.
            Architecture work with Shadrack ongoing.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>WAXFEED</strong> — pre-launch audience and architecture phase.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="now-section">
        <h2>Team</h2>
        <p>
          Theodore Addo, founder. Shadrack Annor, technical director and WAXFEED domain lead.
          Nathan, director of strategy and partnerships. Roles formalized with documented
          scope and compensation structure.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="now-section">
        <h2>What is not happening</h2>
        <p>
          No fundraising for the sake of fundraising. No pivots. No expansion of scope before the
          first IΔ contract closes. The lab is not a startup optimizing for growth — it is a
          research lab proving a methodology, one instrument at a time.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>

    <p class="now-footer">
      This page follows the <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">now page convention</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .now-page {
    max-width: 640px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 2rem 6rem;
  }

  .now-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .now-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-pure);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .now-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: var(--text-ghost);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .now-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
  }

  .now-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    margin-bottom: 0.875rem;
  }

  .now-section p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .now-section p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  .now-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .now-section li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .now-section li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--text-ghost);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .now-section strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .now-footer {
    margin-top: 3.5rem;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-ghost);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-ghost);
  }

  .now-footer a {
    color: var(--text-ghost);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .now-footer a:hover { color: var(--teal); }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .now-page { padding: 3rem 1.25rem 4rem; }
  }
</style>
